data.description: Gorgeous curb appeal and a pristine interior welcome you home to an open-concept floor plan, easy-to-care-for tile floors, and a  dedicated home office that can be used as a first-floor media room as well. Four spacious bedrooms and an additional second-floor living room provide ample space for all. The tucked-away, main-level secondary bedroom, and full bath are ideal for hosting overnight guests. The kitchen island features grey cabinetry, paired with white quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and an extended breakfast bar which enhances the open concept. The first-floor primary bedroom is a private haven featuring crown molding, separate vanities, a separate shower, a large garden tub, ample storage, and two walk-in closets. Also, be sure to make use of the upstairs loft area which can serve as a fun game room, craft space, or a more casual lounging area. Come see this lovely home now and make it your own!
